external_knowledge:
Top 5 most downloaded implies packages with the highest value in the downloads_count column; 
latest version refers to the version with the highest release date for each package; 
unresolved issues or pull requests means packages where issues or pull_requests column is greater than 0.

sql:
SELECT package_name
FROM packages
ORDER BY downloads_count DESC, package_name ASC;

SELECT p.package_name
FROM packages p
ORDER BY p.downloads_count DESC, p.package_name ASC;
